Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, anybody have any questions? We'll proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's the question line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my question is, when you mentioned early on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, just speak normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, 15% of people on the planet are above, like, 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, just curious, if that isn't set in stone, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if that's been increasing, and that increasing is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said during the lecture, the consciousness level of mankind at the time of the birth of Buddha was 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of the birth of Jesus Christ, the consciousness level of mankind was at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it evolved to 190, yes, 190, over the centuries, 1200s, 1300s, Middle Ages, until the late 1980s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About 1987, at about the time of the Harmonic Accordance, it suddenly jumped from 190 to 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I understood that, but is that due to a higher percentage of people being above 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you could have just a different distribution to cause the overall average...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I can tell you, the collective consciousness, that's what it calibrates at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:02:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, besides maintaining unconditional love, compassion, and compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,kindness in everything you do, is there other things you can do to help protect from appearances of the lower astral realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, speak up. Repeat it, but ask it a little bit louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book, you talk about the lower astral realm, and there are dark forms that sometimes appear and try to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the lower astral realms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides maintaining unconditional love and compassion and kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything else you can do to help protect yourself from their appearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just be the most evolved being that you can be, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you know, everybody has karma, righto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people you strangle to death, and you don't think you're going to choke some night, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. So we've got to figure it ourselves, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept your karma with good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I would pray, that's all. You just pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are many invocations, you know, and the white light and all those kind of things, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, that which is negative hates that which is positive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so you just be as positive as you can be, and they'll find you repulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of an individual couple here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we, by our choices, reduce regress from 400,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to below 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people evolve, and other people devolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I should devolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have past karma that I need to apologize to you for,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for a past lifetime that's been muscle tested many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it wise for people in this position to apologize in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They already killed me in one lifetime. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We exchange favors, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you this time, you kill me next time. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't cause anything, then enlightenment is by virtue of the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And does that mean that we can't do anything to cause enlightenment or to further our enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't cause it. That's force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You align yourself with it, rather than trying to force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, it's more a yin posture than a yang pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, when it stands forth, it's like a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand back, and it reveals itself to you, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It just presents itself. It's not something you grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality presents itself overwhelmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year ago, I was in Sedona, and I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you told me two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One was I needed serious psychological help.
