Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been working on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So to that end, I don't have a question today.
