Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I get your intention.
