Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.29,0:28:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So your mother says to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.29,0:28:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own life, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.29,0:28:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the whitewash in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.29,0:28:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, geez, Ma,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.29,0:28:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to play ball with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.29,0:28:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, wipe that look off your face, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.29,0:28:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't allowed to have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.29,0:28:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The comfort of being able to have feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.03,0:28:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is what I enjoyed about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.03,0:28:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.05,0:28:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.05,0:28:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.80,0:29:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already asked all my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a certain memory and viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.22,0:29:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,being white's a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.22,0:29:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So stiff and formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.22,0:29:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.54,0:29:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.44,0:29:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm using muscle testing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.20,0:29:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to test the efficacy of a marketing campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.20,0:29:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or the best direction
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to make my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.20,0:29:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I do that without explicitly asking
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.20,0:29:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for a future event,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.43,0:29:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge about a future event?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.54,0:29:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask something, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.54,0:29:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.54,0:29:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on the integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intention of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.83,0:30:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And self-benefit is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.83,0:30:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you ask is in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.76,0:30:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.76,0:30:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you ask that my company develop this product,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.76,0:30:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,employ this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.76,0:30:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,go in this direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.76,0:30:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,would serve the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because the highest good serves everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.85,0:30:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the customer, the purchaser,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the salesman, the manufacturer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.85,0:30:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the owner, the licensor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.62,0:30:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we ask anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.16,0:30:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get an invitation to speak someplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.16,0:30:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we say, these people are integrals.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.16,0:30:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.16,0:30:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it serve the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.16,0:30:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to accept speaking in Dayton?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.16,0:30:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.16,0:30:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we got a no, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason we're here is we got that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.32,0:30:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it serves the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.32,0:30:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has nothing to do with personal preference,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.32,0:30:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do with gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.32,0:30:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can inquire about your company
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.32,0:31:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and say it serves the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.32,0:31:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because who are you serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.32,0:31:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serving employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.32,0:31:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serving the owners?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.32,0:31:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you have a right to profit
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.32,0:31:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,from your own endeavor, too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.32,0:31:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not negated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.32,0:31:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you want to bypass pure selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.32,0:31:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it serves the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.32,0:31:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I usually ask everything in terms of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.32,0:31:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves the highest good to speak in Dayton
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.32,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or not to speak in Dayton.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.68,0:31:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.68,0:31:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it serves the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.68,0:31:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.60,0:31:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.60,0:31:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.74,0:31:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.16,0:31:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.16,0:31:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.92,0:31:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.60,0:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a drink of Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off that camera for one instant
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.60,0:31:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,while I have a drink of Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.60,0:31:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.60,0:31:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.60,0:31:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.60,0:31:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.60,0:31:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.60,0:32:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.70,0:32:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spoken of karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.24,0:32:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't see it as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.24,0:32:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.66,0:32:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.75,0:32:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-moralistic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.75,0:32:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's automatic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.75,0:32:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Morality is one way to look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is just the consequences of your own actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, and your own intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.99,0:32:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can be the same action.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.02,0:32:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,action, but the intention makes it completely different. You know, when that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.52,0:32:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,warrior and I killed each other, we had the same intention. I did it for God, he
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.46,0:32:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,did it for God, and we served each other. Warriors, warriors honor each other. When
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.33,0:32:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the war is over, the first people who shake hands and salute the other are the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.69,0:33:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,warriors. The men at Armistice sign the officers, the men of each side, salute
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.41,0:33:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,each other. They salute each other's honor because each one did it for the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.78,0:33:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,honor of serving God and country, the king, whatever. Yeah, so war is not what it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.47,0:33:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,looks like on the surface. Many hidden aspects to war are the undoing of negative
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.11,0:33:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,karma, crossing over below 200 to above 200, valor, service, honor, many things
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.61,0:33:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,involved in war. A simple person, you know, just says all war is bad. Yeah, right, you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.61,0:33:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be alive if it weren't for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.99,0:33:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you had freedom if it weren't for war. So, okay, you'd all be dead. If it weren't for war, you wouldn't be alive. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.29,0:33:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for many people in St. Louis. I'm carrying you back. I got a hug from St. Louis. That's neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you have a foundation in what it does. I mean, do you have, do you have some sort of a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.50,0:34:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,foundation?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.12,0:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you just, are you just speaking on a speaking tour? Or do you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.32,0:34:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,foundation? Some kind of a foundation? Oh, we have a nonprofit research
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.06,0:34:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,institute, yes, Institute for Spiritual Studies, yes. Oh, that's all? We publish all the books. So that you, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.70,0:34:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,basically what you do. I mean you don't... We write, we do research, we publish books,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.16,0:34:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we teach, we give lectures, yes. I was a little bit disturbed by the answer to the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.74,0:34:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,question of the previous lady that asked about Africa and the, your
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,your idea of the karma of a young baby that suffered all the things that you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.12,0:34:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.12,0:34:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you blaming the baby for a prior life?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.12,0:34:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about karma. How are you going to understand the negative karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.12,0:34:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, it's the baby's fault that it's being chopped up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.12,0:34:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fault. No, you're interjecting. I didn't say anything about fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.12,0:35:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said fault. I didn't say anything about fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.12,0:35:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm trying to understand what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.12,0:35:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I said karma. Karma is, by your own intention, you become this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.12,0:35:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.18,0:35:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a way of separating yourself from that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.18,0:35:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You create a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.18,0:35:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it convenient to separate yourself from the suffering in that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.18,0:35:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, to just say, oh, that's happening over there. I'm not involved in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.86,0:35:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose karma is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.86,0:35:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about karma. I don't quite understand. I mean, I wouldn't just accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.86,0:35:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come out of nothingness? How did you arise as who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it necessarily that I pick up something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.86,0:35:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some kind of karma? That's like heliotropism is a definition of something that doesn't tell me anything. It's just a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.86,0:35:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you explain your own existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.43,0:35:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to. Why would I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.50,0:35:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you asking any question right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.50,0:35:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here right now celebrating it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.50,0:35:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You doubt it already. Otherwise, you wouldn't be asking me a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.50,0:36:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be certain about the nature of your own existence and its source, and it answers its own questions, and you have no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'm happy to be here dancing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.50,0:36:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.50,0:36:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst thing is you don't understand the concept of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.50,0:36:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you haven't explained it to me, is what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd have to be a student. You know, it takes a little while to understand karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.50,0:36:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is the consequence of...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.88,0:36:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's like heliotropism. You have to get a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.88,0:36:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. You're trying to ridicule it. Instead, you're not asking a question. You're coming up to ridicule me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.88,0:36:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask a question, I'll teach you what karma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.88,0:36:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.88,0:36:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma is an ancient knowingness from the ancient East.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.88,0:36:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's verifiable through calibrating levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.71,0:36:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not commonly accepted in the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.71,0:36:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it is commonly accepted in the Western world in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.90,0:37:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That when you leave this physicality, you will suffer the consequences of your decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.90,0:37:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spiritual decisions in this lifetime will decide whether you go to heaven or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.90,0:37:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Jesus Christ said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.90,0:37:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Jesus Christ and the Buddha and Krishna and all the great avatars...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.90,0:37:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if you found yourself in hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.90,0:37:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.90,0:37:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't advise it. I asked for God to get me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.90,0:37:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you changed it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.90,0:37:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.90,0:37:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think that that might be what we might want to do for those children in Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.90,0:37:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Change hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.90,0:37:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Change their situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.90,0:37:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go ahead and change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.90,0:37:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.90,0:37:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.90,0:37:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.90,0:37:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.25,0:37:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.25,0:37:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, I wonder if you have to soak your arm at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.63,0:37:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Arianne Pacey still alive, or is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.94,0:37:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.94,0:37:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne Pacey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.94,0:37:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne Pacey?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.94,0:37:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.07,0:37:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne Pacey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.07,0:37:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.07,0:37:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne Pacey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.07,0:37:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.07,0:37:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't hear she.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.07,0:37:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my best friend's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.07,0:37:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been missing since, for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.07,0:37:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.07,0:38:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.07,0:38:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.07,0:38:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.07,0:38:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.07,0:38:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.07,0:38:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.07,0:38:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.07,0:38:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.07,0:38:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.07,0:38:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.07,0:38:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.26,0:38:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.26,0:38:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne, Arianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.50,0:38:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been missing for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.50,0:38:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.63,0:38:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.63,0:38:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.63,0:38:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Any way I can find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need to know for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.63,0:38:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It would ease my friend's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.63,0:38:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then it's your friend's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.63,0:38:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.63,0:38:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It would ease my suffering to ease hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.63,0:38:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're joining in sort of an identification with the situation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.95,0:38:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.95,0:38:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.95,0:38:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.95,0:38:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.95,0:38:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.95,0:38:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah okay well we'll talk to you later that's a personal question I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.64,0:39:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if I permission to answer you see I'm not gonna do that in public thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.44,0:39:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about some of the things that you said today yes working on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.30,0:39:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of all coming from the same nothingness and the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.27,0:39:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about what has then what is the meaning of the experience of personal choice and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.63,0:39:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was looking at the ideas that you talked about of all of all experience
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.89,0:39:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everything coming from nothingness the movements whatever and at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.89,0:39:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibility of having choice and where there's the personal it's the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.23,0:39:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning of being an individual fit into that structure of all coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.71,0:39:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness your question doesn't make sense it's a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.71,0:39:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,semanticist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.37,0:39:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not a question what is the question I'm working on the expert what
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.20,0:39:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is the meaning of the experience of being an individual what is the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:40:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of experience you mean in a generic sense or you personally for me personally
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.02,0:40:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the only person I can invest that seems to be the only thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.02,0:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can address yeah so what is the question and then I'm thinking and also
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.04,0:40:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to understand the idea of all being part of coming from the same
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.30,0:40:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness and all coming from I didn't say we come from nothingness I didn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.92,0:40:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm sorry I said thoughts arise from nothing it's thought arises from
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.29,0:40:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing okay I didn't say we arise from nothingness that's not a possibility we
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.03,0:40:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,arise from allness but again the same is it the same allness the infinite allness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is by definition allness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.62,0:40:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,allness context what you know each of us at the same time is different half it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.31,0:40:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has different experiences yes at least in our awareness that's correct have in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.11,0:41:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,our awareness we have different experiences I'm trying to correlate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.71,0:41:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,differences which I interpret as separation but at experience is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,separation yeah yeah experience is a separation when I know when I at least
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.19,0:41:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectually understand that there is no separation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah and I'm trying to make sure you're asking me from an ontologic level I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.01,0:41:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,believe that I understand the sense of the meaning of that word yeah the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.74,0:41:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,significance of beingness itself in existence is that what you're asking in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the context of the difference between being that being sensed individually
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.64,0:41:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this or being that I sent being senses being individual being this or being
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that then is up to personal choice and that comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:42:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of divine ordinance and yet we're all part of the same diviner or not
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the same allness divine ordinance calibrates at an infinite level of course yes and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.53,0:42:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,yours probably doesn't calibrate over a thousand right sure yeah and so it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.73,0:42:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all reflections of the diamond you know it's like each one of us is a reflection of the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.98,0:42:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,same primordial truth that is the essence of all of us yes a dimension of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all a different dimension of the same thing thank you each one of us is a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.60,0:42:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,reflection of the diamond you know why it should be I don't know that's divine
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.99,0:43:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,will divine will that it should be so thank you I like divine ordinance you can
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.72,0:43:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,just blame it all on God and you're done with it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.73,0:43:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is about karma yeah no I while you were speaking you expressed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.80,0:43:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it quite a knowledge of your past lifetimes and I've wondering how
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.06,0:43:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,important you feel it is or how helpful it would be for a person to be aware of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.18,0:43:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,some of their past karma and if so how do you figure out what
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.83,0:43:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what they might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.33,0:43:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma in past lifetimes is a whole lecture in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.87,0:43:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty advanced, sophisticated level.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.21,0:43:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.31,0:43:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly one becomes aware that there's not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.57,0:44:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,individual separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.99,0:44:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one life with various incarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.21,0:44:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you remember the incarnations
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.77,0:44:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because each one of them had usually
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,had a very profound and significant spiritual lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.40,0:44:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.67,0:44:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you remember them very specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.73,0:44:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember them very specifically, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.86,0:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, before that happens, very often one intuits it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost like you intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.58,0:44:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I must have been so-and-so
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because of this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.88,0:44:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, there's various ways of investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.72,0:44:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go into past life research.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.52,0:44:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a very simple technique of self-hypnosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.16,0:44:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which I could teach you, in which you go down
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.40,0:44:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you ask the question, and you get in the elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.30,0:44:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get off the 10th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.36,0:44:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the experience that you're asking for reruns.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.22,0:45:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.02,0:45:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You re-experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.30,0:45:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's past life recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.10,0:45:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is various technicians of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.90,0:45:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,various hypnotists and various therapists
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.60,0:45:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who specialize in past life recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.96,0:45:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's very helpful to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.92,0:45:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a very specific problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.00,0:45:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A very specific symptom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.10,0:45:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A very specific symptom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.35,0:45:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you recall that, it will relieve the symptom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.58,0:45:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually a forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.62,0:45:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually a forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.46,0:45:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.68,0:45:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're interested in past life,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.95,0:45:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it explains karmically perhaps why
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,certain things are happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.30,0:45:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I use the example.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.58,0:45:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sitting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.36,0:46:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I use the example of going through surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.56,0:46:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Without anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.56,0:46:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And one time I was going through surgery without anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.20,0:46:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for an inguinal hernia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.84,0:46:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the pain was excruciating.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.54,0:46:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of this excruciating pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.52,0:46:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I recalled the warrior that I speared right through the groin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.30,0:46:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did not do the coup de grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.83,0:46:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not relieve his agony by cutting his throat or killing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.31,0:46:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.51,0:46:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I left him to die of his wounds and agony, which takes weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.08,0:46:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The guilt of that lasted all these lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.92,0:46:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All these lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.22,0:46:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I undid the karmic pain and agony
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of what I subjected him to through moral cowardice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.22,0:46:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.28,0:46:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The warrior owes the other warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.98,0:46:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the honor of handing him the gun with a single bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.36,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in if he wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.80,0:47:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's up to the warrior to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.70,0:47:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was my failure of moral courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.30,0:47:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have executed the coup de grace out
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.68,0:47:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of saluting his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.29,0:47:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I punished myself by going through exactly what
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.37,0:47:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he experienced, agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.36,0:47:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That began to run in the middle of surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.40,0:47:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.16,0:47:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what I'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.32,0:47:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologized to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.47,0:47:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I'm sorry that I lacked the moral courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.23,0:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The coup de grace, which is, you wouldn't understand probably
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.01,0:47:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as a woman, but as a man, coup de grace
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.07,0:47:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is what I owe my fellow warrior as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.23,0:47:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.73,0:47:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.26,0:47:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter who you're fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.02,0:47:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I, as a warrior, or you as a warrior, got courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.93,0:47:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I failed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.68,0:47:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that guilt lasted all these lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.62,0:47:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a chance to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.22,0:47:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, it might be something specific like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.64,0:47:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a certain symptom in your stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.62,0:47:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, in which past life recall
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.50,0:48:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,might be useful in relieving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.46,0:48:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, it's a forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.26,0:48:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, it's a forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.52,0:48:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.12,0:48:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to forgive myself for having failed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.76,0:48:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I apologized to his spirit that I failed you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.53,0:48:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel sadness about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.83,0:48:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.88,0:48:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.38,0:48:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of our girls that volunteered to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.18,0:48:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.50,0:48:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.50,0:48:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.51,0:48:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.39,0:48:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she wants a hug, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.76,0:48:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the girls that helped put this all on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.28,0:48:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much, sweetheart, for putting this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.24,0:48:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.73,0:48:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My question of the two United States
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.93,0:49:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,presidential candidates, George Bush and John Kerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.41,0:49:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the late 1800s?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.69,0:49:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The current election, 2004.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.65,0:49:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,On a scale of 1 to 1,000, a logarithmic scale of 1
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.01,0:49:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to 1,000, what are the individual calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.65,0:49:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.11,0:49:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.77,0:49:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the individual calibrations of those two
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.65,0:49:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,presidential candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.65,0:49:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you to find out, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.42,0:49:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach you kinesiology, and you can do your own research.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.99,0:49:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that for the common good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.99,0:49:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.96,0:49:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May the best man win.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.79,0:49:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is being president good karma or bad karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.55,0:49:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.99,0:49:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I would consider it bad karma for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.91,0:49:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but for somebody else, it might be good karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.19,0:49:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.69,0:49:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,About five years ago, my energy was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.53,0:49:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.09,0:49:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,About five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.75,0:49:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About five years ago, my energy was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.79,0:49:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.83,0:49:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My kundalini energy was released,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.63,0:50:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't realize what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.99,0:50:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And through a kinesiologist in Atlanta,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.35,0:50:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she put me in touch with some masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.79,0:50:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the energy in my body 24 hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.63,0:50:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes it's very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.27,0:50:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see things I don't understand, and I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.70,0:50:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of at the end of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.72,0:50:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.82,0:50:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.32,0:50:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And they answer a lot of questions for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.26,0:50:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you don't see people individually anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.56,0:50:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know if you can give me any kind of guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.94,0:50:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as to what I might do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.52,0:50:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling it kundalini energy to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what everybody has told me that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.56,0:50:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.94,0:50:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what everyone has told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.56,0:50:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's what everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.00,0:50:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.50,0:50:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.09,0:50:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd want to give her some disease she doesn't have,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.04,0:50:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like wild crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.86,0:50:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.88,0:50:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the kundalini energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.30,0:50:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the energy rises and falls in my body a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.86,0:51:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But then when during the day or, well, 24 hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.54,0:51:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sleep very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.98,0:51:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it pull and tug in my body
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.72,0:51:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through different things, like it's trying to clear things.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.58,0:51:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.08,0:51:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I feel like it's.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.58,0:51:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're saying, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.88,0:51:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a therapist that you're working on with this, balancing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.40,0:51:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,energy, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.96,0:51:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked with a couple of, through the kinesiologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.76,0:51:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked with a couple of masters from Malaysia.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.80,0:51:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a Methodist.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.16,0:51:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have very much residence
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.12,0:51:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for that part of what they're telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.06,0:51:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.34,0:51:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen a psychiatrist, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.30,0:51:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.92,0:51:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.70,0:51:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.46,0:51:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.54,0:51:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, each person in society has a function, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.24,0:51:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time you need a dentist,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.58,0:51:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,time you need a psychiatrist, time you need a priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.88,0:51:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,time you need somebody to bury you, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.06,0:51:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the talents, whatever they can offer, each one offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.60,0:51:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of the puzzle, and then it sort of fits together.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.32,0:52:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I got something with psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.46,0:52:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something from introspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.76,0:52:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something from university.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.42,0:52:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something from the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.22,0:52:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something from all those things, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.72,0:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a mosaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.44,0:52:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you put together what you can learn from each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.46,0:52:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the answer seems to come out of the composite.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.11,0:52:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough information yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.89,0:52:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.73,0:52:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the information to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.35,0:52:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going on with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.33,0:52:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.83,0:52:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.33,0:52:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.15,0:52:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The masters tell me the answer is within myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.65,0:52:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that I should meditate.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.57,0:52:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anybody can tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you that for 5 and 1 half cents, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.73,0:52:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.23,0:52:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.73,0:52:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.89,0:52:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.39,0:52:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.89,0:52:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you're telling me, these random energies that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.82,0:52:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are not leveled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.16,0:52:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would ask a psychiatrist what he thinks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.46,0:52:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.40,0:52:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will just consult masters on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.12,0:52:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and other wild and crazy things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.10,0:52:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.63,0:53:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you know, I would consult somebody professionally
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.15,0:53:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,trained also, who's aware of human brain physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.29,0:53:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotions and acupuncture systems and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.47,0:53:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and can put it together for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.19,0:53:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have it together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.61,0:53:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.45,0:53:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there's something missing from your puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.37,0:53:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they told me I've had a lot of trauma and accidents
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.79,0:53:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.29,0:53:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but those are generalities, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.11,0:53:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are generalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.03,0:53:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.59,0:53:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask personal questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.97,0:53:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was the only way I got to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.71,0:53:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but that's.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.31,0:53:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.81,0:53:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.31,0:53:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.79,0:53:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.29,0:53:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.79,0:53:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.29,0:53:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're missing in the answer, then, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.33,0:53:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to search for somebody who can add to the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.41,0:53:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get the whole puzzle together,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.89,0:53:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,then it sort of makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.19,0:53:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.11,0:53:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.61,0:53:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.27,0:53:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.73,0:53:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.83,0:53:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful for you and Susan and the whole staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.19,0:53:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.69,0:53:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at your last seminar and said I just love the love.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.25,0:53:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read your three books, and I'm just very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.63,0:54:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a, you made a statement that I, maybe you could
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.39,0:54:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,clarify, you can't transcend until you master it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.95,0:54:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.45,0:54:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, if I'm wanting to move toward 500 and 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.31,0:54:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,do I read books?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.83,0:54:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I ponder that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.57,0:54:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do I master the intellect in some way, which seems a little harder to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.41,0:54:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you're saying, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.33,0:54:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a matter of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.13,0:54:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say that intention will bypass many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.11,0:54:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways, it's easier to jump from the 300s to the 500s
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.97,0:54:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,than it is to go all the way through the 400s, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.99,0:54:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize that the Newtonian paradigm is not
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.73,0:54:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate reality, you've already taken a giant leap over the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.31,0:54:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.37,0:54:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize that 500 is unconditional love, 500 is love, 540
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.93,0:54:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is unconditional love, you say, well, what groups teach unconditional love?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.63,0:55:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are the premises that get them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.21,0:55:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the 12th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.65,0:55:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step groups are probably the best demonstration of 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.79,0:55:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best demonstration of 600 or so is miracles groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.63,0:55:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, if you really want to evolve spiritually,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.69,0:55:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would practice the 12 steps and do miracles, the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.25,0:55:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do that wholeheartedly, you'll automatically be that, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.48,0:55:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.32,0:55:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it means that if you have any grievance, the 10th step,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.24,0:55:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you apologize for having to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.62,0:55:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You apologize for having any grievance or having misspoken yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.78,0:55:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You pray through the 11th step through meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.02,0:55:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, awareness of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.41,0:55:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You become responsible to your human, everybody around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.01,0:55:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,by trying to be as loving and forgiving as you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.85,0:55:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And automatically, you're in the 500s, because that's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.15,0:55:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what the people in the 500s are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.31,0:55:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to be aware of the sacredness of all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.75,0:56:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to be of goodwill towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.19,0:56:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see a little black beetle in an alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.55,0:56:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's lying on his back, you can't help but take a twig
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.23,0:56:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and help him to go over, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.15,0:56:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intellect says, that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.49,0:56:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But your heart says, if your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.77,0:56:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you walk by this black beetle, and he's flapping like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.01,0:56:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's helpless, you get hit with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.69,0:56:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.82,0:56:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get more than five paces.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.28,0:56:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, your intellect says, it's only about a bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.64,0:56:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's on its way out, and it doesn't mean anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.58,0:56:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But somehow, guilt tugs at you that you have failed its appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.98,0:56:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, your heart pulls you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you turn the beetle over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.24,0:56:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do that, your intellect says, that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.52,0:56:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, you feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.64,0:56:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you can't bypass the beetle anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.06,0:56:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then you know you're over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.58,0:56:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.70,0:56:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.94,0:57:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.30,0:57:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll make you a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.70,0:57:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of the Black Beetle League.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.38,0:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the sport jacket, too, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.21,0:57:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we will no longer bypass black beetles
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.29,0:57:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with their little arms waving in the wind, we'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.29,0:57:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help, help, give me a twig, and say, oh, thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.43,0:57:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.91,0:57:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Little black beetles praying, oh, help me, God, help me, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.93,0:57:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help, help, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.01,0:57:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And along comes the twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.46,0:57:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Harkins, for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.28,0:57:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And bless you for doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.16,0:57:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned in 1987 that the Harmonic Concordance raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.84,0:57:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, at the time of the Harmonic Concordance.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.88,0:57:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.52,0:57:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not caused by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.34,0:57:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The mankind's consciousness raised over the 200 mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.60,0:57:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from 190 to 205, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.98,0:57:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, can the 15% at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.40,0:57:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the apex of the pyramid come together
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.96,0:58:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with a unified effort of loving kindness, world peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.18,0:58:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.68,0:58:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.28,0:58:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or one consciousness, and effect a quantum leap
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.41,0:58:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that we might see peace in our time?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.37,0:58:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's too mechanistic of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.45,0:58:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking at it from causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.49,0:58:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but this causing it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.71,0:58:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's that the 15% by their buoyancy tends
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.71,0:58:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to pull up the whole field by their buoyancy, by what they are
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.61,0:58:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and not what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.79,0:58:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So they couldn't get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.75,0:58:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know who each other is, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.47,0:58:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But the intention, you see, the intention of over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.15,0:58:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.70,0:58:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's common to over 200 is truth and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.68,0:58:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's common to below 200 is what I feel and what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.60,0:58:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And over 200, they teach you what you feel and what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.40,0:58:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is nice, but it's really irrelevant to the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.66,0:58:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,answer for mankind, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.96,0:59:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So over 200, you mean to sacrifice personal selfishness,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.54,0:59:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and under 200, personal selfishness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.90,0:59:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is supposed to be given dominance, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.26,0:59:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the combined intention is like a buoyancy
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that pulls up the whole field by what it is, not what it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.46,0:59:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.52,0:59:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.34,0:59:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So karma is like a cork, like a cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.08,0:59:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And every choice, so I didn't really
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.40,0:59:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,finish the lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.02,0:59:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, you know, the infinite field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.59,0:59:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a giant electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.81,0:59:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of us is born karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.69,0:59:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,like a little magnetized particle.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.73,0:59:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will automatically go into the field
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.13,0:59:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of that which we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.05,0:59:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are automatically determines
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.95,0:59:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where you go in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.03,0:59:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.19,0:59:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're shaped like this, you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.13,0:59:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're shaped like this, you go there, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.63,1:00:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.77,1:00:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which you have become through your own intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.01,1:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,by your own choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.45,1:00:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By your own sin, determines where you will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.73,1:00:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're like a cork.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.85,1:00:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So a cork that says yes, yes to love floats high.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.69,1:00:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And one that rebukes love, says love is a weakness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.51,1:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's despicable, and hatred is better,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.33,1:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,will sink to the bottom, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.51,1:00:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of that which they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.11,1:00:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a consequence of a punitive god.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.61,1:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a consequence of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.51,1:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a punitive god is just a depiction of duality projected
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.32,1:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on to causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.64,1:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a depiction of God, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.64,1:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.98,1:00:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.86,1:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.36,1:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.31,1:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that line is gone, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.93,1:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.23,1:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.99,1:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is a personal one, physically,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.00,1:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which would hopefully benefit the rest of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.28,1:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in its unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.20,1:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For years I've been struggling with some low back pain, which
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.60,1:01:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe is due to a disruption of the second chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.86,1:01:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And issues there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.24,1:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the second chakra?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.96,1:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the energy center around the sacrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.68,1:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.54,1:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this being asks your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.52,1:01:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to help assist dislodge that disruption
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.76,1:01:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow for a free flow of energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.84,1:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's blocking it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.61,1:01:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the issues of the second chakra
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.73,1:01:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,tend to be of sexual energy and its expression into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.65,1:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for me, that's one of the issues that I've been wrestling
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.99,1:01:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with in proper expression of these energies
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.05,1:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in a creative way that isn't a.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.87,1:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you try breathing it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.23,1:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.83,1:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.33,1:01:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.83,1:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.29,1:01:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it as an energy flowing up the chakra system.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.75,1:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And breathe it out of that chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.13,1:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And breathe it up to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.34,1:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it up to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.96,1:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.52,1:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like a slap in the head instead of a hug today, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.94,1:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He would like a what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.06,1:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A slap in the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.90,1:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.60,1:02:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted a slap in the head instead of a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.64,1:02:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.24,1:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.74,1:02:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.08,1:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.78,1:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.36,1:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.60,1:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he's young.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.50,1:02:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get older, you won't have to complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.67,1:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Age will cure it, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.27,1:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How come there's, um, I find myself on this list,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.75,1:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,both at the bottom and at the top,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.27,1:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I realize that most of the calibrations
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.21,1:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that you give, you give one number.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.25,1:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.99,1:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How does what work?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.55,1:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here, and there, and there, and there, and there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.95,1:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, those are just passing emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.33,1:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.67,1:03:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lifestyle, what you stand for,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.69,1:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your prevailing attitude towards life
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.06,1:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,will tell you where you are in the field there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.14,1:03:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevailing, prevailing, you know, moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.42,1:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just passing emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.76,1:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.26,1:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.89,1:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.77,1:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicate your life to what you live by.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.32,1:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tells you where you are, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.66,1:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If your life is dedicated to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.00,1:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,getting even with somebody, then you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.72,1:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,know you're dedicated to hatred, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.88,1:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.66,1:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you know, you can tell by what the dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.54,1:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of your life is to, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.58,1:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, boy, that gives me hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.96,1:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's hope for you, or you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.22,1:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be up here asking a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.80,1:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.20,1:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.08,1:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.58,1:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.56,1:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be up asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.40,1:03:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be up asking a question
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.24,1:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you weren't aligned with self-improvement
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.94,1:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcending wherever you're at, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.26,1:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.48,1:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted a moment of your attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.84,1:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.02,1:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.04,1:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.54,1:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How much I appreciate your wisdom, your wit, humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.12,1:04:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.62,1:04:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you share it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.76,1:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.46,1:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a blessing just to have you ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.12,1:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.24,1:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.30,1:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to get a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.32,1:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.04,1:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.00,1:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine indeed, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.30,1:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.80,1:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.30,1:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.54,1:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.88,1:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.74,1:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See how many beautiful people come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.56,1:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.69,1:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.19,1:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.69,1:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, would you please comment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.93,1:04:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on the calibration of some of the Sufi masters, such as Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.61,1:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you them specifically,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.87,1:04:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm not a Sufi student.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.57,1:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember Rumi is high, yes, high.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.45,1:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 600 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.67,1:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.63,1:04:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not into Sufi masters much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.87,1:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have time to study such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.02,1:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.52,1:05:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.02,1:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.52,1:05:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.85,1:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I wasted my life on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.31,1:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many things I haven't had time to study yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.31,1:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.31,1:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.62,1:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.18,1:05:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sufi is your head at the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.34,1:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.09,1:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.01,1:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just have to come back and do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.55,1:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.63,1:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Never say no, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.13,1:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.63,1:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the date and there's still time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.46,1:05:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know if I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.04,1:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.16,1:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I spent so many years doing psychiatry,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.88,1:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.54,1:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.16,1:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like to give thanks to you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.78,1:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming here today and sharing your knowledge and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.62,1:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely has raised my level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.04,1:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, you mentioned that music
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.98,1:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,has a calibration of 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.58,1:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular music, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.84,1:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, have you ever done any calibration on,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.76,1:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, quote, quote, rap music or?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.46,1:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.11,1:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what has that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.25,1:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a lot of music.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.67,1:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a lot of music.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.67,1:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.17,1:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The book that we're going to publish.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.79,1:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We did many famous musicians, from Rachmaninoff to Beethoven.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.29,1:06:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We did recent pop artists, operas.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.85,1:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We did Count Basie, people like that, basic jazz people.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.83,1:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Current rap does not calibrate very high, gutter rap,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.16,1:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,calling women whores.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.72,1:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicking pregnant ladies in the belly does not calibrate very high.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.20,1:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you actually do any calibration on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.34,1:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.96,1:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're quite low.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.51,1:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, each level of society has its own music.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.70,1:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And from the top to the bottom, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.18,1:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And to express such negativity so grossly calibrates low.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.82,1:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.32,1:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it glamorizes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.12,1:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.72,1:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It glamorizes violence.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.90,1:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.14,1:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.74,1:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't so much what's alluded to is the glamorization of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.44,1:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That you should be this way, you'll be hip, you'll be a star.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.08,1:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the seduction of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.64,1:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the seduction of the glamorization of negativity
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.14,1:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is where the error is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.78,1:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've seen some rap musicians come on and say, correctly,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.20,1:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that they came out of poverty into, you know, wealth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.82,1:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.06,1:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think, OK, now that you've got that,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.00,1:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,now you should become a pattern for identification
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.50,1:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for what is beyond just money gain, you know, and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.40,1:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I understand that they're saying
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.58,1:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a way out of the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.92,1:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate that, that that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.76,1:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In your final analysis, has there
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.50,1:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,been a correlation between the negativity of the rap
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.40,1:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the low consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.86,1:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.36,1:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Low consciousness, let's say, of the African-American community?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.86,1:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to do with African-American.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.86,1:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the glorification of that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.60,1:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.52,1:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the strong masculine honors women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.31,1:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak masculine despises women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.87,1:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak masculine fears women and despises them, denigrates
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.71,1:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,them, calls them whores, or captivates them,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.22,1:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and keeps them subjugated without the right
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.36,1:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to own property or vote, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.80,1:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong masculine loves women and honors them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.32,1:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would teach them to move from the weak masculine
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.84,1:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to the strong masculine, which loves women, sees their beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.81,1:09:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,their intrinsic value and worth, that they nurture life,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.01,1:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and honor that which nurtures life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.29,1:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that way, you would move from the bottom to that which is,,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.53,1:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,uplifting, to nurture life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.21,1:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they begin to appreciate and honor women, not as sex
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.59,1:09:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,figures, to dance around for erotic entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.57,1:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but for the value of that which they contribute to human life,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.01,1:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,where would you be without the woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.99,1:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be born yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.11,1:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.39,1:09:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The results are coming out in your next book,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.23,1:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the study of the abusing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.13,1:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the guy who despises women, he says, without woman,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.23,1:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't even be here to complain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.59,1:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,about women, young man, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.47,1:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.59,1:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.59,1:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the womb comes men, W-O-M-E-N.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.78,1:09:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 15 minutes to do five people.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.08,1:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.40,1:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'd like to say I appreciate that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.64,1:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.14,1:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is about fluctuation
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.02,1:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.44,1:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how else to, I'll use an analogy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.08,1:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you say that if someone reads your book,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.12,1:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and I imagine any of the books, it's transformative.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.74,1:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, The Power Versus Force,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.88,1:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're, you know, the average consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.56,1:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 35 points that it increases.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.34,1:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's say someone reads that book,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.32,1:10:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they go about their business.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.82,1:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They watch 70,000 hours of reality TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.10,1:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they steal a burger from Burger King.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.98,1:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does their, just, you know, I'll just throw that out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.32,1:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but does their consciousness level fluctuate?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.26,1:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a decrease?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.66,1:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because you always have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.28,1:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every instant, the mind is making a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.22,1:10:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Every instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.78,1:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Every instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.62,1:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at every instant, every instant,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.90,1:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is automatically making a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.76,1:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.58,1:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a little hummingbird, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.58,1:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower, this flower, this flower, this flower.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.34,1:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's constantly going like so.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.18,1:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can watch consciousness as it flicks,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.74,1:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,making its choices, you know, to that which it is attracted,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.98,1:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.09,1:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, that which you esteem is that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.31,1:11:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,attracted to, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.27,1:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So like I was telling you the last gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.03,1:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you esteem, you're attracted in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.33,1:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you esteem women, then you honor them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.89,1:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you, you know, otherwise you disgrace them, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.03,1:11:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if I could just add to that a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.97,1:11:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so, and I imagine, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.43,1:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,someone wouldn't steal a Whopper, probably,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.23,1:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if they were going to read Power Versus Force, but.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.67,1:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone would?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.73,1:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't steal a burger, I would imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.15,1:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, steal a burger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.33,1:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.83,1:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.33,1:11:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they were hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.18,1:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they may, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.38,1:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.42,1:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal a burger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.22,1:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We could start a bunch of shops called Steal a Burger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.46,1:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal a burger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.06,1:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.94,1:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a dollar in here, and you get to steal anyone there,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.28,1:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.78,1:12:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's say, you know, there are days where sometimes someone
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.24,1:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,might feel more connected to source, or to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.48,1:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.98,1:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there are other days where they just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.54,1:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you just, you don't feel that so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.28,1:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.14,1:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a, is that symptomatic of,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.43,1:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, a consciousness level that has decreased,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.93,1:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that one day it was higher?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.99,1:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, it's just a hummingbird, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.95,1:12:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the choices are within a certain limitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.99,1:12:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're not choosing to stab somebody to death today.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.49,1:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they're still only within a mild range.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.43,1:12:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as your consciousness level moves,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.81,1:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your range moves up to a different level, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.65,1:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The little bug with his legs waving in the air is only going
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.53,1:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to bother you at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.26,1:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Below that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.80,1:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Below that level, you're not even going to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.32,1:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in this level, you're going to get caught in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.94,1:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this, beyond this level, you see, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.04,1:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you transcend all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.30,1:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference whether you give it a twig
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.46,1:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or not to give it a twig.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.86,1:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so let's say someone's at 510 today.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.92,1:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A month from now, they can't be at 505.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.16,1:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.00,1:13:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.30,1:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.42,1:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did, the fellow sawed his arm off
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.36,1:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,during the intermission.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.86,1:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on TV last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.20,1:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The story, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.58,1:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.56,1:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain climber who fell into a crevasse,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.68,1:13:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and a big rock imprisoned his arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.05,1:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the rock fell on his arm, he calibrated,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.31,1:13:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission, OK, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.39,1:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to share this with the audience, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.37,1:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The privacy of the audience, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.82,1:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he calibrated at 250.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.36,1:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To go mountain climbing, you've really got to be around 250.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.92,1:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The rock fell on him, and the level at which he
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.80,1:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,sawed off his arm was 505.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.38,1:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He realized he had to saw off his arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.32,1:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow he energized the divine energy of God, the courage,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.64,1:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and he jumped to 505.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.04,1:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time he sawed off his arm, he calibrated at 505.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.20,1:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He has since evolved even further to 510, 510, 515.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.63,1:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 510, 515.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.81,1:14:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 510 already.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.83,1:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So he jumped from 250 to 510.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.69,1:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, that would take you about 500 lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.27,1:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it in one lifetime in a matter of days.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.42,1:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's written a book on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.78,1:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, it's quite a story of valor and courage,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.20,1:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.78,1:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, few of us would be willing to saw off our arm
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.62,1:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to jump from 250 to 510.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.68,1:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.20,1:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do handshakes?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.92,1:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I do handshakes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.92,1:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.42,1:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.95,1:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we all salute that young man's courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.65,1:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Really quite something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.61,1:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You had mentioned in your book that there are six or seven
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.91,1:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,people that have reached a level of 600 in the world right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.33,1:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.07,1:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.25,1:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.03,1:15:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.41,1:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.79,1:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of them?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.41,1:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want to be bothered with your mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.08,1:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep looking then.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.08,1:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.58,1:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It fluctuates, because they sometimes come out,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.18,1:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they topple over.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.01,1:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They arrive, and then they leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.05,1:15:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then some crash, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.63,1:15:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.91,1:16:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk about dreams from sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.95,1:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they purely a result of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.91,1:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and where the ego is at that time in consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.23,1:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it something more?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.03,1:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done the amount of research
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.73,1:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to do on dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.41,1:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten that it's mainly brain physiology that's
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.35,1:16:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,going on, that it's mainly brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.89,1:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream is mainly, primarily brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.89,1:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty much brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.61,1:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote a critique of Freud's interpretation of dreams
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.85,1:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.71,1:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, the dream was a production of the brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.11,1:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a story, and then the story acts like a Rorschach card.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.67,1:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you associate it with the brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.83,1:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,when you lie on the couch and pre-associate to the dream,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.17,1:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really like it's a Rorschach card.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.73,1:16:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you project into the Rorschach card
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.81,1:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is meaningful to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.19,1:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And dreams are very profoundly informative in psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.25,1:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember when I transcended the edible complex,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.79,1:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and it came as a horrific case of terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.63,1:17:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in to see my analyst one time, and I lay on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.35,1:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I had such an anxiety attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.79,1:17:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.31,1:17:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety was getting worse and worse by the weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.15,1:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The worse the anxiety got, I couldn't drive over the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.29,1:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't drive through a tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.67,1:17:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had claustrophobia.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.07,1:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And my analyst was very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.18,1:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He was pleased at the great progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.68,1:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So one day, I go to lay on the analyst.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.38,1:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I lay on the couch, and I had an acute anxiety attack,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.38,1:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the great granddaddy of all anxiety attacks,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.38,1:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,an absolute terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.55,1:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.89,1:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told him the dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.09,1:17:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this lion.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.39,1:17:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all by myself, and there's some woman in the background,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.39,1:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and this lion attacks me and kills me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.19,1:17:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, what does that make you think of?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.61,1:17:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.87,1:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind went blank.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.59,1:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, do you know any lions?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.37,1:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I don't know any lions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.19,1:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, what's my name?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.65,1:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, Lionel Obesee, my psychoanalyst
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.94,1:18:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was the father figure, who was going to kill him, castrate,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.72,1:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,me, because I had a fantasy about stealing his wife
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.28,1:18:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.96,1:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it came out of the unconscious, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.58,1:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you, the anxiety attack was real.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.08,1:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And his name was Lionel Obesee.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.56,1:18:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a lion that came to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.08,1:18:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the brain is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.22,1:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then once I went through that dream,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.80,1:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the analysis of that dream, the edible conflicts and all
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.22,1:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.92,1:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that time, I've had no conflict with men
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.02,1:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or competition with men.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.04,1:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or power, concerns about power, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.64,1:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So the psychoanalysis was complete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.50,1:18:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and successful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.22,1:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it came as a crashing climax to a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.50,1:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were asking about dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.04,1:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you what my personal experience is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.12,1:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.64,1:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.14,1:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than theory, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.64,1:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have five minutes and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.36,1:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.10,1:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are just going to be finishing up perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.02,1:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be real quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.10,1:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.50,1:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband and I are big students
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.12,1:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of all your work, as well as Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.28,1:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Toronto a couple of months ago to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.04,1:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.64,1:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we drove down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.86,1:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're wondering, what can we do to get you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.02,1:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to come to Ann Arbor, Michigan?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.12,1:19:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann Arbor, Michigan?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.44,1:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're coming in next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.32,1:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.04,1:19:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're scheduled for Michigan, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.06,1:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a schedule for Michigan next year, but I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.38,1:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.06,1:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to Michigan in so many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.94,1:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in Wisconsin, and we used to take the Clipper across
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.41,1:19:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to Muskegon, and the family owned a little cottage
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.53,1:19:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,up in Iron Mountain, Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.43,1:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't been in there, been to Michigan in 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.97,1:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,probably, so I would enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.49,1:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we would love to have you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.79,1:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.09,1:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.39,1:20:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.73,1:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.60,1:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.90,1:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.28,1:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to do in Michigan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.72,1:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a couple we have already.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.74,1:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.04,1:20:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Ann Arbor?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.34,1:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Bearers used to, we had a cottage up there
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.24,1:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you went out around the garbage can,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.36,1:20:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you had to chase the Bearers away.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.34,1:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were speaking earlier of intention and forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.38,1:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.34,1:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you if we utilize our intention
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.79,1:20:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to use forgiveness or to invoke forgiveness for ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.19,1:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and for other people to work through karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.19,1:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is that an effective tool for doing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.57,1:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.07,1:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.51,1:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, in the sense of can it dissolve,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.36,1:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not the word I'm looking for,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.86,1:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,can it neutralize that negative karma or that type of karma
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.06,1:21:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's making up for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.28,1:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, because otherwise nobody would ever
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.12,1:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to evolve spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.74,1:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you take responsibility, you ask for forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.36,1:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and you choose the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.36,1:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you use prayer, you ask God's help.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.18,1:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I like what they teach in the Course of Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.20,1:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're really asking is the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.42,1:21:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to recontextualize the thing so that you can see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.92,1:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask for a miracle, what you're saying is,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.52,1:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I'm seeing it is limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.98,1:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask God to show me the total picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.70,1:21:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the total picture, you realize there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.22,1:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.58,1:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only by seeing it is limited, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.32,1:21:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When the lens expands, you see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.86,1:21:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing, you see that everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.18,1:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is in a development over time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.84,1:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you look at content only,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.72,1:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're taking it outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.90,1:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you see the whole picture,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.46,1:22:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the development.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.86,1:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now over time, permanently, it all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.40,1:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.20,1:22:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't necessarily alleviate life lessons
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.06,1:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or the type of learning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.40,1:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it gives you an explanation by completing the picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.00,1:22:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see the complete picture,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.54,1:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize there's nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.88,1:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives us a chance to recontextualize.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.62,1:22:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.16,1:22:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.66,1:22:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.16,1:22:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.16,1:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's say the third one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.16,1:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.50,1:22:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name's Diane.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.82,1:22:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from Michigan to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.02,1:22:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.46,1:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.70,1:22:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank Susan, because just watching her
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.14,1:22:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and her love and devotion is just inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.52,1:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I also wanted to know when your next book
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.90,1:22:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was coming out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.98,1:22:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.76,1:22:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be in my lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.80,1:23:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it'll be in your lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.28,1:23:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope by the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.40,1:23:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've had to write it and rewrite it and rewrite it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.02,1:23:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what the difficulty is.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.52,1:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our world has become so contentious
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.96,1:23:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't mention any subject
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.78,1:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without bringing up all kinds of energy about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.58,1:23:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you say, well, I can express it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.06,1:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can't express anything
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.38,1:23:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that there isn't a parade about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.56,1:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are you going to tell people the truth of things
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.56,1:23:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,within the world when they all have
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.02,1:23:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a vested positionality about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.71,1:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't ask what is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.83,1:23:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What they want you to do is to validate what they believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.59,1:23:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.27,1:23:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then lastly, when you leave this body, when you come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.65,1:23:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I left already.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.59,1:24:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I came back today just for you folks here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.99,1:24:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.95,1:24:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.93,1:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you in this regard.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.38,1:24:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.54,1:24:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.36,1:24:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you all, devotively.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.10,1:24:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O God, do I surrender my life, my beingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.35,1:24:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I open myself to the revelation of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.69,1:24:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of thy presence as the source of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.41,1:24:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes the position, the prayer, the supplication,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.79,1:24:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the surrender, because you are the field and not
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.79,1:24:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the content of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.25,1:24:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You become one with the field, which cannot resist
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.33,1:24:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the mudra of the question, because that which
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.57,1:25:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is being asked is the very source of your existence
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.41,1:25:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore cannot refuse.
